+-------[F2] Menu for Server Management-------------------+
| 00     Clear screen                                      |
| infooo Server info + benchmark                           |
| sos    SOS default (24h)                                 |
| sos1   SOS 1 hour                                        |
| sos3   SOS 3 hours                                       |
| sos24  SOS 24 hours                                      |
| sos120 SOS 120 hours                                     |
| stat   WireGuard traffic statistics                      |
| backup Run backup                                        |
| fight  Block bots                                        |
| domains Check domains                                    |
| antivir Show CrowdSec bans                               |
| banlog Show CrowdSec alerts                              |
| load   Update from GitHub                                |
| save   Save to GitHub                                    |
+----------------------------------------------------------+
